hs]]\n[[Category:Bangladeshi film directors]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the National Film Awards (Bangladesh)]]\n[[Category:Bangladeshi television directors]]\n[[Category:Bangladeshi male writers]]\n[[Category:Bangladeshi film producers]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox person\n| name          = Syed Salahuddin Zaki\n| native_name   = \u09b8\u09c8\u09af\u09bc\u09a6 \u09b8\u09be\u09b2\u09be\u0989\u09a6\u09cd\u09a6\u09bf\u09a8 \u099c\u09be\u0995\u09c0\n| birth_date    = {{Birth date and age|1946|08|26}}<ref name=\"dt5Jan2019\" />\n| birth_place   = Tangail, [[British India]]<ref>{{cite book |editor1-last=Noble |editor1-first=Peter |editor2-last=Moore |editor2-first=Oscar |year=1991 |title=Screen International Film and Television Yearbook 1991/92 |publisher=International Thomson Business Publishing |page=35 |isbn=1-85032-044-6}}</ref>\n| nationality   = Bangladeshi\n| occupation    = Music director, film lyricist\n| years_active  = 1980\u2013present\n| notable_works = [[Ghuddi]]\n| spouse        = \n| family        = \n| awards        = [[National Film Awards (Bangladesh)|National Film Award]] (1st time)\n}}\n\n'''Syed Salahuddin Zaki''' is a Bangladeshi film director, producer and film writer.<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/salahuddin-zaki-returns-hena-1369855|title=Salahuddin Zaki returns with \u201cHena\u201d|date=March 3, 2017 |work=The Daily Star}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.thedailystar.net/news/all-the-worlds-a-stage|title=All the world's a stage|date=July 19, 2013 |work=The Daily Star}}</ref><ref name=\"dt5Jan2019\">{{Cite news |url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/showtime/2019/01/05/ghuddi-director-syed-salahuddin-zaki-hospitalized |title=\u2018Ghuddi\u2019 director Syed Salahuddin Zaki hospitalized |date=January 5, 2019 |work=Dhaka Tribune}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.newagebd.net/article/66374/12th-intl-childrens-film-festival-begins |title=12th Int\u2019l Children\u2019s Film Festival begins |work=New Age